reviewText: We have all watched this tape at least 100 times already with my 2 year old granddaughter, who LOVES this tape....  It came in just as described in the ad and in a very timely matter....  Very pleased with the seller!!!!

I was disappointed. This video lacked originality, and the personality the first two have. No gymnastics, no personal messages, and the songs were dull and uninspiring. Too much special effect. I'm sorry, I just didn't like it.
